{"tid":1660320,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得 大家無謂再糾纏霖霖單野度","createTime":"2019-10-17T12:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T17:00:25.000Z","uid":230681,"like":37,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"16c12cc5845ff942824014d961543d121568c2b7","tid":1660320,"uid":230681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:22:52.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔值得查唔值得提<br />\n但老實講 人地老母都話佢唔想再追究<br />\n<br />\n一來 真係班狗殺既 俾咗掩口費既<br />\n佢老母就算打撚都唔會講架啦<br />\n<br />\n二來 佢話個女有思覺失調 姐係有精神病<br />\n淨係呢一句 基本上都無得打<br />\n<br />\n我知死咗人 仲要咁細個大家都好唔開心 我都係<br />\n但而家根本冇仼何對我地收利既證據<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰琴晚俾人扑 人權案仲未過<br />\n幾千個手足等緊上庭 條路仲好長<br />\n不如放眼未來 做大啲做盡啲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人，反抗</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">10.20 13:30 尖沙咀見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFqbbH6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFqbbH6.jpg&h=34235eba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/He1qf9P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHe1qf9P.jpg&h=8fef3272&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/stbxFBy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FstbxFBy.jpg&h=e9aaa3a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtuLf9V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmtuLf9V.jpg&h=b94dd88b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gken2P0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGken2P0.jpg&h=b13a6a3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e39052213e331835cbb20a4d85d421490a6ae2e0","tid":1660320,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockq